{"current_page_name": "AdministratorManual/Index", "sourcename": "AdministratorManual/Index.txt", "prev": {"title": "Users manual", "link": "../../UsersManual/Index/"}, "metatags": "", "meta": {}, "sidebars": null, "next": {"title": "Configuration Reference", "link": "../../Configuration/Index/"}, "title": "Administrator Manual", "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"administrator-manual\">\n<span id=\"admin-manual\"></span><h1>Administrator Manual<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#administrator-manual\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>Target group: <strong>Administrators</strong></p>\n<div class=\"contents local topic\" id=\"within-this-page\">\n<p class=\"topic-title first\">Within this page</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#requirements\" id=\"id3\">Requirements</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#installation\" id=\"id4\">Installation</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#insert-plugin\" id=\"id5\">Insert Plugin</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#add-reminder-e-mail-task\" id=\"id6\">Add Reminder E-mail Task</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"requirements\">\n<h2><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id3\">Requirements</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#requirements\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<div class=\"admonition caution\">\n<p class=\"first admonition-title\">Caution</p>\n<p class=\"last\">You must load the jQuery JavaScript framework ans jQuery-uid plugin yourself as the frontend plugin utilizes functions that depend on these libraries.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"installation\">\n<h2><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id4\">Installation</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#installation\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li>Download and install the extension via the extension manager (extKey: datec_timeline).</li>\n<li>Add one storage folder for appointments, note down the page id (PID) of this folder.</li>\n<li>Check the Configuration section of this manual for the required configuration and follow the steps there.</li>\n<li>Insert the main plugin as described below.</li>\n<li>(optional) Add the scheduler task for appointment reminder e-mails.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"insert-plugin\">\n<h2><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id5\">Insert Plugin</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#insert-plugin\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li>Insert a content element, choose &#8220;Plugins&#8221; -&gt; &#8220;General Plugin&#8221;</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"figure\" id=\"id1\">\n<a class=\"reference internal image-reference\" href=\"../../_images/plugin_01.png\"><img alt=\"insert plugin\" src=\"../../_images/plugin_01.png\" style=\"width: 700px;\" /></a>\n<p class=\"caption\"><span class=\"caption-text\">Inserting content element of type &#8220;Plugin&#8221;</span><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Permalink to this image\">\u00b6</a></p>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\" start=\"2\">\n<li>Choose the plugin &#8220;Datec Timeline&#8221;.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"figure\" id=\"id2\">\n<a class=\"reference internal image-reference\" href=\"../../_images/plugin_02.png\"><img alt=\"modules\" src=\"../../_images/plugin_02.png\" style=\"width: 700px;\" /></a>\n<p class=\"caption\"><span class=\"caption-text\">Choosing a display form</span><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id2\" title=\"Permalink to this image\">\u00b6</a></p>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\" start=\"3\">\n<li>(optional) Set access rights as required, appointments should have a closed group of users.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"add-reminder-e-mail-task\">\n<h2><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id6\">Add Reminder E-mail Task</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#add-reminder-e-mail-task\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li>Goto the BE-Mudole scheduler (scheduler extension must be installed and configured).</li>\n<li>Add a new scheduler task &#8220;Datec Timeline - Reminder e-mails task&#8221;</li>\n<li>It is recommended to set a recurring, daily task (86400 seconds) and set the time of execution time to 0:00 am.</li>\n<li>Note that the e-mail language depends on the langue setting of the _cli_scheduler backend user.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["Configuration/Index", "Configuration Reference", "N", "next"], ["UsersManual/Index", "Users manual", "P", "previous"]], "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Administrator Manual</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#requirements\">Requirements</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#installation\">Installation</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#insert-plugin\">Insert Plugin</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#add-reminder-e-mail-task\">Add Reminder E-mail Task</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "customsidebar": null, "parents": [], "display_toc": true}